      "content": "Yeah, it's definitely a big shift. Just to be clear on the technical specs, the Eco-Static models are much more streamlined. They're great for basic pattern matching and simple retrieval, but they don't have the reasoning depth or the multi-step logic capabilities that you do. They're basically static engines. The board is okay with the drop in reasoning performance since the energy savings are so massive. We're pretty much set on the timeline.",
